reviews.text:
I've vaped quite a bit of this stuff, it's quite good. I've also tried the earlier version of this, the BRY4 Bourbon IIRC. I'm giving it a 4-star review but the only reason is because I find the flavor to be a bit too weak, so I'll try upping the total flavoring for myself next time I mix this. &#xD;
&#xD;
On the other hand, it should be a huge compliment that I've mixed this 3-4 times (including the earlier variant), because I almost never mix most recipes that I try again, since I'm one of those people that doesn't really have an ADV and just keeps mixing new shit all the time. So good job on the recipe!
